title: TMPGEnc 4.0 XPress v4.7.1.284 Retail
description:
TMPGEnc 4.0 XPress v4.7.1.284 Retail | 30.06 MB

The new version of the popular video editor - TMPGEnc 4.0 XPress, who uses a high-quality codec MPEG 1 / 2 as well as DivX. Through thoughtful design of the program you will not be a problem in order to encode the video. For best results, you will be available for most popular codecs including DivX 6 AVI, QuickTime, MPEG 4-ISO, H.264, DVD-Video, DVD-VR, HDV recording with the camera, and many others. Also, you can upload videos on your mobile device: PSP, iPod or PDA, using the MPEG-4 ISO and H.264 formats. The program also contains a lot of additional settings, as well as video filters and special effects.

OS: Windows 98/ME/2000/XP/2003/Vista
